import cadquery as cq

inner_radius = 10
outer_radius = 40
thickness = 20
cog_count = 6
cog_width = 20
cog_height = 10
cog_insert_depth = 2

gear = cq.Workplane("XY").circle(outer_radius).circle(inner_radius).extrude(thickness)

cog = cq.Workplane("XY").rect(cog_width, cog_height).extrude(thickness)
cog = cog.translate((0, 0, -cog_insert_depth / 2))

for i in range(cog_count):
    angle = 360 / cog_count * i
    cog_pos = (outer_radius - cog_width / 2) * cq.Vector(cq.Vector(1, 0, 0).rotated((0, 0, angle)))
    gear = gear.union(cog.translate(cog_pos))

r = gear

import cadquery as cq

inner_radius = 10
outer_radius = 40
thickness = 20
cog_count = 6
cog_width = 20
cog_height = 10
cog_insert_depth = 2

gear = cq.Workplane("XY").circle(outer_radius).circle(inner_radius).extrude(thickness)

cog = cq.Workplane("XY").rect(cog_width, cog_height).extrude(thickness)
cog = cog.translate((0, 0, -cog_insert_depth / 2))

angle = 360 / cog_count
cogs = [cog.rotate((0, 0, 0), (0, 0, 1), i * angle) for i in range(cog_count)]

for cog in cogs:
    gear = gear.union(cog)

r = gear
